  "Description": {
    "English": "A thermal regulator produced from refined organic material. It is unique in its ability to produce, dissipate and distribute heat as required.<br><br>Crafted from <span class=\"name name-special\">Solanium</span> and <span class=\"name name-technology\">Frost Crystals</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一种由精制有机材料生产的热量调节器。其具有独特的生产力，驱散和分配所需的热量。<br><br>由<span class=\"name name-special\">日光茄</span>和<span class=\"name name-technology\">冰霜水晶</span>制作。",
    "TencentChinese": "一种由精制有机材料生产的热量调节器。其具有独特的生产力，驱散和分配所需的热量。<br><br>由<span class=\"name name-special\">日光茄</span>和<span class=\"name name-technology\">冰霜水晶</span>制作。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "以精製有機物質生產的熱能調節器，具有獨特功能，可按要求製造、發散和分配熱能。<br><br>可使用<span class=\"name name-special\">日艸</span>和<span class=\"name name-technology\">霜晶</span>製造。"
  },
