  "PinObjectiveTip": {
    "English": "Craft from <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">Frost Crystals</span> and <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">Solanium</span>. Learn the blueprint with the aid of a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Science Specialist</span> in a base.<br>Frost Crystals can be farmed, or found wild on <span class=\"name name-technology\">frozen planets</span>.<br>Solanium can be farmed, or found wild on <span class=\"name name-fuel\">scorched planets</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "由<span class=\"name name-technology\">冰霜结晶</span>和<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">日光茄</span>制作而成。在基地中，在<span class=\"name name-technology\">科学专家</span>的帮助下学习设计图。<br>冰霜结晶可以通过种植获得，也能在<span class=\"name name-technology\">冻土星球</span>上找到。<br>日光茄可以通过种植获得，也能在<span class=\"name name-fuel\">烧灼星球</span>上找到。",
    "TencentChinese": "由<span class=\"name name-technology\">冰霜结晶</span>和<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">日光茄</span>制作而成。在基地中，在<span class=\"name name-technology\">科学专家</span>的帮助下学习设计图。<br>冰霜结晶可以通过种植获得，也能在<span class=\"name name-technology\">冻土星球</span>上找到。<br>日光茄可以通过种植获得，也能在<span class=\"name name-fuel\">灼热星球</span>上找到。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "以<span class=\"name name-technology\">霜晶</span>及<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">日光茄</span>製作。在基地裡借助<span class=\"name name-technology\">科學專家</span>來了解設計圖。<br>霜晶可以在<span class=\"name name-technology\">冰寒星球</span>上栽種或於野外採集。<br>日光茄則可以於<span class=\"name name-fuel\">焦土星球</span>上栽種或於野外採集。"
  },
